    "data": {
      "rank": "basic",
      "description": "<h2>INFUSIONS</h2><p><strong>Also:</strong> Arcane Ammunition, Blade Coatings, Combat Runes.</p><hr /><p>When you hit one or more targets with an attack, you may spend @LOSS[2 ip] to produce a special <strong>infusion</strong> and apply the corresponding effect to that attack (if the attack had the <strong>multi</strong> property, apply the effects of the infusion to each target).</p><p>You cannot apply more than one infusion to the same attack; producing and using an infusion are both part of the action you used to attack with the weapon.</p><p></p><h3>BASIC INFUSIONS</h3><table style=\"width:100%\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width:80px\" data-colwidth=\"98\"><p><strong>INFUSIONS</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>EFFECT</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width:80px\" data-colwidth=\"98\"><p><strong>Cryo</strong></p></td><td><p>The attack deals 5 extra damage, and its damage becomes <strong>ice</strong> @ICON[ice].</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width:80px\" data-colwidth=\"98\"><p><strong>Pyro</strong></p></td><td><p>The attack deals 5 extra damage, and its damage becomes <strong>fire</strong> @ICON[fire].</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width:80px\" data-colwidth=\"98\"><p><strong>Volt</strong></p></td><td><p>The attack deals 5 extra damage, and its damage becomes <strong>bolt</strong> @ICON[bolt].</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><h3>ADVANCED INFUSIONS</h3><table style=\"width:100%\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width:80px\" data-colwidth=\"98\"><p><strong>INFUSIONS</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>EFFECT</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width:80px\" data-colwidth=\"98\"><p><strong>Cyclone</strong></p></td><td><p>The attack deals 5 extra damage, and its damage becomes <strong>air</strong> @ICON[air].</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width:80px\" data-colwidth=\"98\"><p><strong>Exorcism</strong></p></td><td><p>The attack deals 5 extra damage, and its damage becomes <strong>light</strong> @ICON[light].</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width:80px\" data-colwidth=\"98\"><p><strong>Seismic</strong></p></td><td><p>The attack deals 5 extra damage, and its damage becomes <strong>earth</strong> @ICON[earth].</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width:80px\" data-colwidth=\"98\"><p><strong>Shadow</strong></p></td><td><p>The attack deals 5 extra damage, and its damage becomes <strong>dark</strong> @ICON[dark].</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><h3>SUPERIOR INFUSIONS</h3><table style=\"width:100%\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width:80px\" data-colwidth=\"96\"><p><strong>INFUSIONS</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>EFFECT</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width:80px\" data-colwidth=\"96\"><p><strong>Vampire</strong></p></td><td><p>Choose one option: you recover an amount of HP equal to half the HP loss suffered by the target of the attack; <strong>or</strong> you recover an amount of MP equal to half the HP loss suffered by the target of the attack.</p><p>This infusion can only be used if the attack targeted <strong>a single</strong> creature.</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width:80px\" data-colwidth=\"96\"><p><strong>Venom</strong></p></td><td><p>The attack deals 5 extra damage, its damage becomes <strong>poison</strong> @ICON[poison], and each creature hit by the attack suffers <strong>poisoned</strong>.</p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
      "basicInfusions": [
